parameters:
\SE[2] Ah... that's 'futanari'. You got caught up in
Lunaroa's 'magic'.

\SE[22]I got dragged into this...!? \!\SE[11]And why is she
creating such a ridiculous magic anyway...!?

\SE\SE[2]Well, well, there were various circumstances...
\SE[3]But thanks to that, I was able to obtain this house.
\SE\SE[2]It's not something to be said lightly, right...?
\SE[3]After all, we are the ones benefiting from it.

\SE[20]I-Is that so... \!\SE[82]...So, do you know how to
make this disappear?

\SM[nod]\SE\SE[0]Ah, it's such a bother, right? I
understand, I understand. \SE[0]It's easy. If you satisfy it
and feel refreshed, it should naturally disappear.

\SE[4]Ah, sorry. It's 'ejaculation'. If you release semen
into the 'core' of magic, it won't be able to maintain its
form and will disappear.
\SE[22]Haa...!? You want me to do something like that!?

\SE[2]Then why don't you try talking to Lunaroa? I think
Laura will be with her, so the two of them can help you.
\SE[1]I also got refreshed by them before.
\SE[94]You want me to ask those two...!?

\SE[14]No, it's definitely not good... \!\SE[15]It's not
good to easily get caught in the gap...

\SE[2]When it's me, I feel a flat vibe, but when it's Vega,
I feel a serious vibe coming out...

\SE[4]Well, I have plenty of sympathy, so if Vega wants,
shall I help her?

\SE[90]...I'm starting to calm down a bit. \SE[83]Is it
difficult to handle it alone?

\SE[15]Hmm, it might be difficult.... \SE[4]The average age
for mastery is around 12-15 years old, but Vega's thing is
still brand new. \SE[3]Lunaroa also said that she needed to
get used to it.

\SE[2]I can't put it into words well, but there's a trick to
it. \!\SE[3]If you don't understand the flow or the key
points, you might not be able to do it well.

\SE[4]Well, I think trying to figure it out on your own is
also one of the choices. \SE[3]For a while, you might be
stuck with the trial and error approach though...

\SE[82]F-Fine... I understand... I'll ask for your help.
\SE[61]I can't stay like this forever...

\SM[nod]\SE[0]Hmm. Leave it to me. \SE[13]I'm used to it, so
you can trust me...!

\SE[20]Lunaroa.... I'll definitely make you work for free
later...

I have my own room too... but I might prefer... spending
time here with everyone...

...As for Vega, you see. She drinks a lot of water while
studying... so she ends up going to the bathroom... quite
frequently...

When I look at the flames, my heart becomes calm... The
flames here are the most comforting.
